'''Naǧib Meḥfuḍ''' (s taεrabt : نجيب محفوظ) d amyaru amaṣri, ilul di Lqahira ass n 11/12/1911, yemmut daɣ din ass n 20/08/2006.Yella d anaggal maca yura daɣen imagraden yemxallafen, ladɣa deg tfelseft, ɣer tama n wugar n 40 wungalen d wammuden n tullisin. Deg useggas 1988 yewwi arraz [[Nobel]] ɣef lǧal n tlata wunagalen-is icudden gar-asen iwumi qqaren tamakuẓt n Lqahira(1- ''Gar snat n ssṛayat''- 2- ''Ssṛaya n lxiq''-  3- ''Lḥuma n Ssukkariy''a ) anda d-yewwi ɣef tudert di Lqahira, tamanaɣt n Maṣer. Ar tura d netta kan i yewwin arraz-a gar wid yettarun s taεrabt, yerna ula deg Tefriqt d yiwen seg imezwura ur neggit.
Naǧib Meḥfuḍ deg tuget n yedlisen-is yettawi-d s umata ɣef tmetti tamaṣrit i yesleḍ s telqey akked d umezruy n tmurt-is, ladɣa deg tallit n Iferεunen. Maca yettwassen daɣ ɣef tira-s icebḥen, tebna ɣas in’as ɣef ubrid n teẓrilewt (réalisme), maca tegget deg-s tesnalfa (poétique) d teɣmi tarumansit.
Deg useggas n 1995 wten-t  sin irebraben islamẓriyen i iεerḍen ad t-nɣen s lmus ɣef lǧal n yiwen wungal mucaεen i yura di 1959 nni : ''Arraw n taddart-nneɣ'' ; imi tuɣ llan lecyax i d-yeftan belli ameskar  yestehza deg-s ɣef Rebbi, ihi sskfren-t rnan sḥellen idamen-is, maca yemneε, yejreḥ kan, ma d irebraben-nni ttuεedmen s tmettant sɣur udabu n Maṣer.
